  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter>
    <html:p>
    This note serves as a supplement to the other notes which are related to mathematical analysis and optimization. At the moment, I am not going to write a comprehensive note for calculus, but I will write some notes for <fr:link href="/opt-6001/" title="Optimal Control" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/opt-6001/" display-uri="opt-6001" type="local">optimal control</fr:link> which is a direct application of <fr:link href="/calc-0002/" title="Calculus of Variations" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/calc-0002/" display-uri="calc-0002" type="local">calculus of variations</fr:link>.
</html:p>
    <fr:tree show-metadata="false">
      <fr:frontmatter>
        <fr:authors>
