        <fr:title text="Calculus of Variations">Calculus of Variations</fr:title>
      </fr:frontmatter>
      <fr:mainmatter>
        <html:p>
  Calculus of variations is concerned with variations of functionals, which are small changes in the functional's value due to small changes in the function that is its argument. The <fr:link href="/calc-0003/" title="Functional Derivative" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/calc-0003/" display-uri="calc-0003" type="local">first variation</fr:link> is defined as the linear part of the change in the functional, and the second variation is defined as the quadratic part.
</html:p>
      </fr:mainmatter>
    </fr:tree>
