        <fr:title text="Functional Derivative">Functional Derivative</fr:title>
      </fr:frontmatter>
      <fr:mainmatter>
        <html:p>
    In the <fr:link href="/calc-0002/" title="Calculus of Variations" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/calc-0002/" display-uri="calc-0002" type="local">calculus of variations</fr:link>, the functional derivative (or variational derivative) relates a change in a functional (a functional in this sense is a function that acts on functions) to a change in a function on which the functional depends.
</html:p>
      </fr:mainmatter>
