                <fr:title text="Hamiltonian Methods">Hamiltonian Methods</fr:title>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <fr:tree show-metadata="false">
                  <fr:frontmatter>
                    <fr:authors>
                      <fr:author>
                        <fr:link href="/boat/" title="Zihang Zeng" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/boat/" display-uri="boat" type="local">Zihang Zeng</fr:link>
                      </fr:author>
                    </fr:authors>
                    <fr:date>
                      <fr:year>2026</fr:year>
                      <fr:month>3</fr:month>
                      <fr:day>7</fr:day>
                    </fr:date>
                    <fr:uri>https://boatnotabot.com/opt-6005/</fr:uri>
                    <fr:display-uri>opt-6005</fr:display-uri>
                    <fr:route>/opt-6005/</fr:route>
                    <fr:title text="Hamiltonian function">Hamiltonian function</fr:title>
                    <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
                  </fr:frontmatter>
                  <fr:mainmatter>
                    <html:p>
Define the Hamiltonian function at an <fr:link href="/opt-6006/" title="Admissible control" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/opt-6006/" display-uri="opt-6006" type="local">admissible control</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbf {u}]]></fr:tex> by <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[H(\mathbf {x}, \mathbf {u}, \mathbf {p}) = {\mathbf {p}}^ \intercal  f(\mathbf {x},\mathbf {u}) + L(\mathbf {x}, \mathbf {u})]]></fr:tex></html:p>
                  </fr:mainmatter>
                </fr:tree>
                <fr:tree show-metadata="false">
                  <fr:frontmatter>
                    <fr:authors>
                      <fr:author>
                        <fr:link href="/boat/" title="Zihang Zeng" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/boat/" display-uri="boat" type="local">Zihang Zeng</fr:link>
                      </fr:author>
                    </fr:authors>
                    <fr:date>
                      <fr:year>2026</fr:year>
                      <fr:month>3</fr:month>
                      <fr:day>7</fr:day>
                    </fr:date>
                    <fr:uri>https://boatnotabot.com/opt-6008/</fr:uri>
                    <fr:display-uri>opt-6008</fr:display-uri>
                    <fr:route>/opt-6008/</fr:route>
                    <fr:title text="Pontryagin's Maximum Principle">Pontryagin's Maximum Principle</fr:title>
                    <fr:taxon>Theorem</fr:taxon>
                  </fr:frontmatter>
                  <fr:mainmatter>
                    <html:p>
Given a control signal <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbf {u}]]></fr:tex>, denote by <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbf {x}_u]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbf {p}_u]]></fr:tex> the corresponding state and costate trajectories.</html:p>
                    <html:p>
Suppose that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbf {u}]]></fr:tex> is an admissible optimal control. Then <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\forall  t \in  [0, t_f],\forall  \mathbf {v} \in  U_t]]></fr:tex>, <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[H\big (\mathbf {x}_u(t),\mathbf {u}(t),\mathbf {p}_u(t)\big ) \leq  H\big (\mathbf {x}_u(t), \mathbf {v}, \mathbf {p}_u(t)\big )]]></fr:tex></html:p>
                  </fr:mainmatter>
                </fr:tree>
              </fr:mainmatter>
